{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二章讲述秦风八与陈见鬼出场救援的故事。阿水与疯女在终南山与费家\"二剑一刀\"（费澄清、费心肝、费宝贝）激战，以\"疯癫拳\"与\"跌撞拳\"配合\"破锣\"暗语击败对手，但自身亦受伤。随后费家逸空嫡系高手费洪与费晓登场，以千蛇百星剑和十字枪逼得阿水疯女险象环生。关键时刻，丐帮两大护法秦风八（\"钟馗伸腿\"）与陈见鬼（\"阉王伸手\"）出手救人，亮明身份。双方一番谈判破裂后展开激战，费晓与陈见鬼两败俱伤，秦风八以香炉反击费洪的琉璃球暗器后毒发倒地。此时费家年青一代第一高手费丹枫出手，欲杀人灭口。关键时刻萧秋水现身阻止，揭去易容自报姓名。费丹枫虽忌惮丐帮势力，但杀心已决。萧秋水不问自身安危，第一句便问\"我的朋友呢\"，尽显重情重义本色，章末以萧秋水与费丹枫对峙收束。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_feng_nv",
      "text": "破锣！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是费家费洪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "费晓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是费家费晓。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "你俩居然汀败了费家的三个没用的人、就让我们教训教训你们。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "镖师",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "不公平！她俩已战累，你们此时挑战，不公道！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_biao_shi",
      "text": "什么公不公平！看所谓的广东侠女是不是盛的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "好哇！小兔崽子，就算是车轮战，老娘也挑下了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "呸！有胆放马过来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_a_shui",
      "text": "这就对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "你们……究竟是哪一帮哪一派的人……？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "你总听说过'丐帮'吧？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "那你也听说过'丐帮'有两大护法吧？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "两位可是……可是外号'阎土伸手'和外号……'钟馗伸腿'的……两位高人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "我就是'阎王伸手'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "我就是'钟馗伸腿'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "费晓",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "我们费家……跟丐帮素无怨隙，两位因何来汤这趟浑水？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_xiao",
      "text": "因为是你们先惹上我们。这两位……姑娘……是因为救助我们，所以才伤成这个样子的。这原是我们的事，我们当然不能坐视。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "那我们赏面给两位兄台，也不对付这两个婆娘，这下两不相欠，可得了吧？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "费晓",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "为什么不行？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_xiao",
      "text": "不行就是不行。你们已刺了人一枪，又有千奇百怪的剑狙击，差点都害你们弄出人命——就这般算了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "更何况……你们刚才语气中侮辱了萧大哥……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "萧秋水跟你们有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "没有关系。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "家帅裘无意，对萧大哥的印象很好，这趟西来，也无非为了劝萧大哥角逐'神州结义'盟主一事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "冤家宜解不宜结，两位对萧秋水，也并无什么渊源，不如就此算了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "如果费兄这番话，在咱们亮出字号之前说的话，那一切都好商量……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "speaker_name": "陈见鬼",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "等到现在才说，不过是趋炎附势——投人情讲！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "费晓",
      "listener": "char_chen_jian_gui",
      "text": "他妈的的王八羔子，真以为老子怕了你下成？！拼就拼吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": "char_fei_hong",
      "text": "费家的兵器，神奇得紧呀！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "费家的暗器，也不逊色！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "speaker_name": "秦风八",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要呼吸！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": "char_qin_feng_ba",
      "text": "倒也，倒也。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "费洪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我们费家年青一代第一高手：费丹枫。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "text": "住手。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "text": "跟我有关。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你，是，谁？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "text": "我是萧秋水。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你，是，萧，秋，水？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "text": "我的朋友呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_dan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "费丹枫",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "闯得过了我这一关，再到华山去找吧。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    }
  ],
